title: Journey to the Year 3000 - Choose Your Own Super Adventure.pdf
description:
There were two "Choose Your Own Super Adventure" books published, and this is the 1st one, by Edward Packard.  The 2nd one is "Danger Zones" by R.A. Montgomery.  With the Super Adventure books, they added about 40 pages to the standard sized CYOA book.


This book was first published in March of 1987, making it about 27 years old now.  Out of print long enough, it's nice to now pass it on to everyone on tpb.

Enjoy!
